timelineItems.text: Timbers in a 4-1-4-1 defensively right now with Jewbsury sitting in front of the CBs. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Mike Pacific
timelineItems.text: Adi just pulled a Wondo. #SJvPOR

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: What a miss from Adi! A sitter off a cross from Rodney and he fluffs it. Oh my. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Fanendo Adi (Portland Timbers) right footed shot from the right side of the six yard box is high and wide to the right. Assisted by Rodney Wallace.

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Another great save from Ricketts on Atiba Harris. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Attempt saved. Atiba Harris (San Jose Earthquakes) header from the centre of the box is saved in the bottom left corner. Assisted by Jordan Stewart with a cross.
Yannick Djaló (San Jose Earthquakes) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Foul by Diego Chara (Portland Timbers).
Foul by Víctor Bernárdez (San Jose Earthquakes).
Fanendo Adi (Portland Timbers) wins a free kick in the attacking half.

timelineItems.name: Cele Jameson
timelineItems.text: Wait until the 86th minute to bring in Urruti?! I don't understand?! #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Alvas Powell (Portland Timbers) right footed shot from the right side of the box misses to the left.

timelineItems.name: Hoss
timelineItems.text: Adi has owned Bermudez all night long. No! I didn't mean it like that. #SJvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 87’ - Powell with fantastic work to kill clock on right wing. Loses ball. Regains it and heads to goal. His shot rolls just wide. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Ben Hickey
timelineItems.text: For a minute I thought we weren't going to see the standard Adi-Urruti sub! 15th straight game that one has replaced the other. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Harrington for Nagbe. Mikey makes his second appearance of the year (USOC at SKC) on the wing. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Russ Andolina
timelineItems.text: Tommy Thompson on the field 5 seconds - wins a tackle, successfully turns out of multiple pressure. But Atiba Harris. #SJvPOR

timelineItems.comment: Alvas Powell (Portland Timbers) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Foul by Atiba Harris (San Jose Earthquakes).
Matías Pérez García (San Jose Earthquakes) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Foul by Diego Chara (Portland Timbers).

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbros
timelineItems.text: Tommy Thompson is a country singer who sings about achieving your goals. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Soo close for Nagbe there. As close as he’s come to scoring all year. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Matías Pérez García (San Jose Earthquakes) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Foul by Diego Chara (Portland Timbers).

timelineItems.name: carriedunn10
timelineItems.text: Rooting for the Timbers from behind enemy lines! #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Jesse Leineweber
timelineItems.text: Harrington as the time waste sub. A applaud you Porter. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Ben Zemanski has earned every bit of his modest contract tonight. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Matías Pérez García (San Jose Earthquakes) left footed shot from outside the box misses to the left. Assisted by Yannick Djaló.

timelineItems.name: Dan Brunell
timelineItems.text: These are the most defensive subs I've ever seen from Porter. Desperate times... #rctid

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbros
timelineItems.text: Never a bad time for a bicycle kick. I approve Zemanski. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Attempt blocked. Tommy Thompson (San Jose Earthquakes) right footed shot from the centre of the box is blocked.
Foul by Ben Zemanski (Portland Timbers).
Tommy Thompson (San Jose Earthquakes) wins a free kick in the attacking half.

timelineItems.desc: Pablo Pintos (San Jose Earthquakes) is shown the red card.
timelineItems.title: RED CARD: Pablo Pintos sent off for two-footed tackle

timelineItems.name: Sagar Trika
timelineItems.text: RED CARD FOR SAN JOSE #RCTID

timelineItems.name: BJ Clark
timelineItems.text: Weird this is the game Porter decides to park the bus. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Jesse Leineweber
timelineItems.text: DID SAN JOSE JUST BLOW WALLACE'S ACL IN STOPPAGE TIME? #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Pablo Pintos with a horrible tackle on Wallace and given his marching orders. Wallace is hurt. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Pablo Pintos (San Jose Earthquakes).
Rodney Wallace (Portland Timbers) wins a free kick in the defensive half.

timelineItems.name: Robert Jonas
timelineItems.text: From field level, that certainly sounded red card worthy from Pablo Pintos. Brutal tackle. #SJvPOR

timelineItems.comment: Delay in match Rodney Wallace (Portland Timbers) because of an injury.

timelineItems.name: Kip Kesgard
timelineItems.text: Pintos went for water then sat on bench after foul, but he's finally been escorted off to locker. #rctid.

timelineItems.comment: Delay over. They are ready to continue.

timelineItems.name: THIIIIRD MOOOORTGAGE
timelineItems.text: Timbers beating San Jose feels as good as beating Seattle. #rctid

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: And that’s the game with Caleb Porter vigorously pumping his arms and yelling into the crowd. As pumped as I’ve seen him. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Jamie Goldberg
timelineItems.text: That's it. Timbers come back to beat Earthquakes 2-1 #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Nolan
timelineItems.text: 11 winless games in a row. #SJEarthquakes

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, San Jose Earthquakes 1, Portland Timbers 2.

timelineItems.name: Jeff Budke
timelineItems.text: San Jose self destructs, saves Portland's season... #RCTID
